sequenceDiagram
    actor Client
    participant Frontend as Frontend React
    participant Gateway as API Gateway
    participant Auth as Auth Service
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Client->>Frontend: Remplit formulaire (nom, email, mdp)
    Frontend->>Gateway: POST /api/auth/register
    Gateway->>Auth: Proxy requête
    Auth->>Auth: Valide les données (Zod)
    Auth->>DB: Vérifie email unique
    DB-->>Auth: OK
    Auth->>Auth: Hash mot de passe (bcrypt)
    Auth->>DB: INSERT INTO users
    DB-->>Auth: Utilisateur créé
    Auth->>Auth: Génère Access + Refresh tokens (JWT)
    Auth-->>Gateway: {accessToken, refreshToken, user}
    Gateway-->>Frontend: 201 Created
    Frontend-->>Client: Redirection vers le dashboard
